data.revised_prompt: Create an image of an adorable cartoon-style kitten with fluffy fur and bright, curious eyes. The kitten is in mid-air, having leaped energetically off the ground with its tiny paws outstretched. It is attempting to catch a round ball that is floating just out of its grasp. The ball is bright and bouncy, adding a playful element to the scene. The kitten looks determined and completely engrossed in its play. Set this lively scene against a neutral background to focus all the attention on the kitten's playful endeavors.
